{"tid":2021940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有日本人為「願榮光歸香港」做咗日版新編曲","createTime":"2020-05-18T04:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T04:51:30.000Z","uid":281802,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81cc49070201d7a185e44c1ca66ca430200c94d6","tid":2021940,"uid":281802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:43:19.000Z","msg":"為大家介紹，一位日本人singer songwriter珠夢改編並cover了願榮光歸香港，這個版本甚有八十年代中島美雪feel，別有一番味道。<br />\n<br />\nYoutube:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_CfG0d4K34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3_CfG0d4K34&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=91be6086\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3_CfG0d4K34</a><br />\n<br />\n珠夢official website<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shuyu.website/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shuyu.website%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=30b2fa82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shuyu.website/</a><br />\n<br />\n自由を求める香港市民が、街頭で歌っている「願榮光歸香港 (Glory to Hong Kong)」。その想いが日本人にも届くよう、珠夢の訳詩・編曲・歌で日本語版にしました。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/videos/405586023487450/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstudioincendo%2Fvideos%2F405586023487450%2F&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=e688dd3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/studioincendo/videos/405586023487450/</a>"},{"pid":"4b0a93b22b16673664189d89a786548936bf87b0","tid":2021940,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前已經好似聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a97cb566a40c52adf3d66246516d5